            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國訂購更多美國大豆 採購步伐緩慢提速",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國已進一步預訂了至少十船的美國大豆，本季迄今的總採購量超過200萬噸，也在使中國緩慢地靠近上月末與美國貿易磋商期間所達成的目標。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因未獲授權公開表態而要求匿名的知情人士透露，國有農業貿易商中糧集團已訂購了今年至2026年初裝運的大豆。知情人士稱，這些大豆將從美國墨西哥灣和太平洋西北港口裝運。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·川普與中國國家主席習近平10月達成貿易休戰協議，促使中國結束了早前暫停採購美國大豆的做法。然而，儘管中國庫存充裕，且美國大豆價格更高，但北京方面仍需保持穩定採購步伐，才能接近雙方顯然已經達成的採購目標。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9910a797-86e4-3e56-8ad7-be4a9b06a7f5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國方面稱，中方承諾今年至少採購1200萬噸美國大豆，未來三年預計將增至每年至少2500萬噸。中國雖已下調大豆關稅，但尚未正式確認採購承諾。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中糧集團未立即回應彭博的置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本周早些時候，芝加哥大豆期貨受中國將維持貿易休戰的樂觀預期推動，一度漲至17個月高位，隨後部分回吐漲幅。部分交易員指出，美國大豆成本高昂，且當前交易主要由國有實體驅動，而非商業需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Books More US Soy Cargoes as Trade Slowly Gains Momentum</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A8%82%E8%B3%BC%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E8%B1%86-%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E6%AD%A5%E4%BC%90%E7%B7%A9%E6%85%A2%E6%8F%90%E9%80%9F-110937934.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-19 20:05:48",
