            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "荷蘭政府交還安世半導體的控制權 與中國的糾紛顯著緩解",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 荷蘭政府停止其對晶片製造商安世半導體的控制權，讓中國所有人恢復掌控；這將幫助化解與北京的僵局，雙方的糾紛已經開始阻礙世界各地的汽車生產。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷蘭經濟事務大臣Vincent Karremans周三在社交媒體網站X上發帖稱，賦予荷蘭權力阻止或修改安世半導體公司決策的命令已被撤銷，以「展現善意」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博本月初曾報導，荷蘭方面表示，如果能夠確認該公司在中國的工廠交付晶片，荷蘭準備採取這一步驟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：如果中國子公司恢復供應晶片 荷蘭據稱準備放棄對安世的控制</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-eb9addf1-439e-3f4f-9958-16f748ce2308-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此舉標志著爭端顯著緩和，這場紛爭凸顯了供應鏈的全球性特徵，並凸顯了北京日益成長的影響力。儘管安世的晶片並非先進技術，且該公司在中國僅運營一家工廠，但這場爭端仍然對從本田汽車到福斯汽車等汽車製造商造成了影響。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Dutch Hand Back Control of Chinese-Owned Chipmaker Nexperia</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Charlotte Hughes-Morgan.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E4%BA%A4%E9%82%84%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%96%E5%8D%8A%E5%B0%8E%E9%AB%94%E7%9A%84%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E6%AC%8A-%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%B3%BE%E7%B4%9B%E9%A1%AF%E8%91%97%E7%B7%A9%E8%A7%A3-091043802.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-19 19:00:51",
